Package tif

Classes for parsing and manipulating TIFF-based files.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DirectoryIFD
    Represents and manages an Image File Directory (IFD) in a TIFF file, conforming to the TIFF 6.0 specification.
    DirectoryIFD.EntryIFD
    Represents a single Image File Directory (IFD) entry within a TIFF structure.
    IFDHandler
    This IFDHandler parses TIFF-based files by reading and interpreting Image File Directories (IFDs) within the file's binary structure.
    MetadataTIF
    A composite leaf component of the Composite design pattern that encapsulates Exif metadata stored in TIFF-style directories.
    TifParser
    This program aims to read TIF image files and retrieve data structured in a series of Image File Directories (IFDs).
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DirectoryIdentifier
    This program enumerates Image File Directory (IFD) types typically found within TIFF image files.
    TagHint  
    TifFieldType
    An enumeration class of data format types defined in the TIFF specification 6.0 document.

Package tif Description

Classes for parsing and manipulating TIFF-based files.

Supports standard TIFF parsing, including tag extraction, IFD navigation, and metadata analysis.

Since:
1 August 2025
Author:
Trevor Maggs
